To kickstart the May School Holidays and to celebrate Mother’s Day, we’ve partnered with Little Miss Bento to bring you a LIVE workshop by top bento artist Shirley Wong from @littlemissbento!
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Parents are highly encouraged to join their little ones on this workshop that will allow you to bond with your child, hone developing motor skills as well as pique the little ones’ curiosity about all things food!
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Date: 9 May 2020
Time: 3pm

Join us on Instagram LIVE via @furamasingapore
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Order your DIY bento sets from the link in our bio or from  https://furamacitycentre.oddle.me/ -  and https://furamariverfront.oddle.me/ - which comes with all the ingredients necessary to re-create and style your too-cute-to-eat bento.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Each set is priced at $16 and includes a disposable apron, hat and hand protection sleeves.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
